Job Description
Follow up delivery with help of support function within purchasing dept;
• Implement new company procedures and standards templates;
• Manage with bid process from purchasing perspectives;
• Ensure compliance of services/materials delivered by suppliers/subcontractors;
• Manage risks and negotiate cost variance;
Skills
- Experience in purchasing.
- Preferably in hotel
restaurants business .
- Should have the knowledge of local market.
